Package: flipscalar
Title: Permutation Inference for Scalar-Valued Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Aymeric",
           family = "Stamm",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "aymeric.stamm@math.cnrs.fr",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8725-3654"))
Description: A re-implementation of classic inferential tools (point 
  estimation, confidence regions, tests) for scalar-valued data (also 
  known as univariate data) using the permutation framework.
